data.name: XtraReportShowPrintStatusDialog
data.value: Gets or sets a value specifying whether a print status dialog is shown when a document is printed.

data.name: XtraReportSnapGridSize
data.value: Specifies the dimensions of the report designer snap grid.

data.name: XtraReportSnappingMode
data.value: Specifies the mode in which report elements are snapped to each other, when they are resized or being relocated.

data.name: XtraReportSnapToGrid
data.value: Gets or sets a value indicating whether to snap report controls to the grid at design time.

data.name: XtraReportStyleSheet
data.value: Provides access to a collection of styles stored in a report.

data.name: XtraReportStyleSheetPath
data.value: Gets or sets the path to the style sheet contained in a style sheet file.

data.name: XtraReportVerticalContentSplitting
data.value: Gets or sets a value indicating whether report controls outside the right page margin should be split across pages, or moved in their entirety to the next page.

data.name: XtraReportWatermark
data.value: Provides access to a report's watermark settings.
